msgid "Split by bookmarks"
msgstr "Pisah mengikut tanda buku"

msgid ""
"Split a PDF document at bookmarked pages by specifying a bookmark level."
msgstr ""
"Pisah satu dokumen PDF mengikut halaman bertanda buku dengan menyatakan satu "
